trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click"></xref> event of an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click"> </xref> hendelse for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event is raised when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>denne hendelsen oppstår når en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objekt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap>kontrollen klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>

trans-unit.source: To allow a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object to raise the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event, you must first set either the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to `HotSpotMode.PostBack`.
trans-unit.target: Tillate en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objektet til å øke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>hendelsen, må du først angi enten den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen `HotSpotMode.PostBack`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.HotSpotMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: To control the actions programmatically that are performed when a postback <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked, provide an event handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> event.
trans-unit.target: Til å kontrollere handlingene programmatisk som utføres når en tilbakesending <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>er valgt, angi en hendelsesbehandling for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A> property stores a string that is associated with the behavior of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> object when clicked.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>egenskapen lagrer en streng som er knyttet til virkemåten for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>objekt når du klikker.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot.PostBackValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: This string is passed in the ImageMapEventArgs event data when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Denne strengen sendes i Hendelsesdata ImageMapEventArgs når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>klikkes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot>
